     * - cpu_model: 128 bytes buffer → %127[^,] (127 chars + null terminator)
     * - disk_path: 256 bytes buffer → %255[^,] (255 chars + null terminator)
     * - network_adapter: 64 bytes buffer → %63s (63 chars + null terminator)
